        public final void setOutFields(java.lang.String[] outFields)
        Parameters:
        outFields - - The list of fields included in the returned result set. This list is a comma delimited list of field names. If you specify the shape field in the list of return fields, it is ignored. For non-intersection addresses you can specify the candidate fields as defined in the geocode service. For intersection addresses you can specify the intersection candidate fields.
